rmal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望後日會好啲"},{"pid":"1df0b3f146fa64a3c1133a3cdf2b563aa3554f57","tid":270104,"uid":40327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"千其唔好上清境 ！ <br />\n我今日係清境出返黎 ！ <br />\n條路爛得好勁 仲有好多伏位 <br />\n我架車卡左2次 郁唔到要人幫手救車 <br />\n想死咁濟！"},{"pid":"a2564a5a17ff73179d0b52e5158e81c4c8dbc838","tid":270104,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千其唔好上清境 ！ <br />\n我今日係清境出返黎 ！ <br />\n條路爛得好勁 仲有好多伏位 <br />\n我架車卡左2次 郁唔到要人幫手救車 <br />\n想死咁濟！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fbbcb90539444fc754fc50a775127fbf852403","tid":270104,"uid":40327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>千其唔好上清境 ！ <br />\n我今日係清境出返黎 ！ <br />\n條路爛得好勁 仲有好多伏位 <br />\n我架車卡左2次 郁唔到要人幫手救車 <br />\n想死咁濟！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係嚇你  不過你硬要上祝你好運 ！ <br />\n我琴日上到乜都冇開 全部停工停課 <br />\n得d雨境 同霧境睇  又超級大雨<br />\n搞到我同個fd只可以留係民宿鳩hea <br />\n黑到落腳趾尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f39a380c095e10dc50ceda0c7885724b4027a3","tid":270104,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"琴日係清境走左<br />\n已經有泥石流警告<br />\n中途有碎石加泥有封路 <br />\n有鏟車做緊野<br />\n客運 農場都停埋就知幾惡劣<br />\n前日上到去係大雨到乜都睇唔到<br />\n成日就係民宿到<br />\n哂左每人400上落清境台中去訓一晚<br />\n<br />\n自己諗下值唔值得去訓<br />\n今日係台中 時大時細雨 都叫有得去下景點去夜市<br />\n清境真係上左去就屈係入邊冇得走<br />\n<br />\n如果去6日覺得哂一日就冇所謂<br />\n但如果4 5日就諗下博唔博<br />\n<br />\n最後我屌佢老母 洗左千幾蚊 乜都冇得睇又哂時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09db226e3ca1207e1ee6900f8aa1fbc2f39049d5","tid":270104,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真 上到去都好難會靚 應該乜都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前去過清境 條車路都唔算話好闊<br />\n而家係台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過又租左車 又要搵過間酒店 <br />\n幾個學生哥好溶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望後日會好啲</blockquote><br />\n你係包車定自駕?"},{"pid":"ded853b7b60f6064a9d915e7e37b502c065d4db1","tid":270104,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"6月 2x 號去  得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92ae73c2d87b44edeac6f69d91e6d05a8f410ca","tid":270104,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真 上到去都好難會靚 應該乜都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前去過清境 條車路都唔算話好闊<br />\n而家係台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過又租左車 又要搵過間酒店 <br />\n幾個學生哥好溶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望後日會好啲</blockquote><br />\n你係包車定自駕?</blockquote><br />\nKkday 包車 早幾日cancel 有得退一半 <br />\n而家冇得退 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34650cd3efc877b791e2ec2cd43eab05ffdec556","tid":270104,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"7b20d886ac44d44795b5eb7db6fa93f3be6558c8","tid":270104,"uid":33510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T00:27:56.000Z","msg":"今日上去清境<br />\n希望冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbf8e26ac1366d26a76b7406460fc9deb853332","tid":270104,"